name: io.bytes.per.checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  io.file.buffer.size.

name: yarn.app.mapreduce.am.job.committer.commit-window
description:
Defines a time window in milliseconds for output commit
  operations.  If contact with the RM has occurred within this window then
  commits are allowed, otherwise the AM will not allow output commits until
  contact with the RM has been re-established.

name: fs.s3a.retry.limit
description:
Number of times to retry any repeatable S3 client request on failure,
    excluding throttling requests.

name: dfs.content-summary.sleep-microsec
description:
The length of time in microseconds to put the thread to sleep, between reaquiring the locks
    in content summary computation.

name: dfs.datanode.max.disks.to.report
description:
Number of disks to include in JSON report per operation. We will return
    disks with the highest latency.

name: dfs.blockreport.initialDelay
description:
Delay for first block report in seconds. Support multiple time unit
    suffix(case insensitive), as described in dfs.heartbeat.interval.If
    no time unit is specified then seconds is assumed

name: seq.io.sort.mb
hadoop.caller.context.signature.max.size
description:
The caller's signature (optional) is for offline validation. If the
      signature exceeds the maximum allowed bytes in server, the caller context
      will be abandoned, in which case the caller context will not be recorded
      in audit logs.

name: ha.failover-controller.new-active.rpc-timeout.ms
description: Timeout that the FC waits for the new active to become active

name: tfile.fs.output.buffer.size
description: Buffer size used for FSDataOutputStream in bytes.
